ive", "topics": ["Iran", "Geopolitics"]}}, {"id": "2075126287232905569", "url": "https://x.com/JavierBlas/status/2075126287232905569", "text": "MAP OF THE DAY: The South Asian monsoon has now fully covered India (about 3-4 days later than normal). The seasonal rains remain below average, but the gap has narrowed to -15% from -35% a few weeks ago. Next few weeks critical for crops and energy demand. https://t.co/hSSwd9Imfr", "time": "07:53", "author": "JavierBlas", "author_name": "Javier Blas", "followers": 393796, "views": 51155, "likes": 516, "replies": 6, "retweets": 108, "quotes": 5, "bookmarks": 46, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Neutral", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Demand outlook"]}}, {"id": "2075129880531103750", "url": "https://x.com/staunovo/status/2075129880531103750", "text": "#Singapore: oil product inventories fell by 0.119mb w/w to 40.334mb last week #oott", "time": "08:08", "author": "staunovo", "author_name": "Giovanni Staunovo🛢", "followers": 120883, "views": 4601, "likes": 19, "replies": 0, "retweets": 8, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 1, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bullish", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Refining/products"]}}, {"id": "2075148676947906952", "url": "https://x.com/JuneGoh_Sparta/status/2075148676947906952", "text": "Europe: Guys, I am really short of diesel. \n\nUS: Can't help you now, I'm short too.\n\nIndia: I can give you some. Might be Russian crude tainted though.\n\nChina: Exports are allowed again but it's going to be mostly mogas and jet fuel. \n\n#oott https://t.co/6UPDTWuVok", "time": "09:22", "author": "JuneGoh_Sparta", "author_name": "June Goh", "followers": 18022, "views": 54577, "likes": 494, "replies": 22, "retweets": 57, "quotes": 7, "bookmarks": 59, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bullish", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Refining/products", "Demand outlook"]}}, {"id": "2075169689001513301", "url": "https://x.com/TankerTrackers/status/2075169689001513301", "text": "Anticipating a possible imminent resumption of the US Navy blockade, Tehran shipped out no less than 10 million barrels of crude oil and fuel oil overnight.\n\n#OOTT #IranWar #Tankers", "time": "10:46", "author": "TankerTrackers", "author_name": "TankerTrackers.com, Inc.", "followers": 227036, "views": 151062, "likes": 613, "replies": 15, "retweets": 143, "quotes": 15, "bookmarks": 54, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bearish", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Iran", "Supply outlook"]}}, {"id": "2075171973131636912", "url": "https://x.com/Amena__Bakr/status/2075171973131636912", "text": "Several explosions were heard in Iran's Bushehr ‌province on Thursday morning, semi official Mehr news reported. Bushehr ‌is where Iran's nuclear power plant is located. #OOTT", "time": "10:55", "author": "Amena__Bakr", "author_name": "Amena Bakr", "followers": 174705, "views": 15232, "likes": 70, "replies": 0, "retweets": 9, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 4, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bullish", "emotional_sentiment": "Negative", "topics": ["Iran", "Geopolitics"]}}, {"id": "2075198301742272882", "url": "https://x.com/IliaBouchouev/status/2075198301742272882", "text": "Another huge 450mb volume of Brent options but most deals are structured as tight multi-legged spreads,  condors, and flies. Oil options are becoming a variation of binary prediction mkts but they are played by pros with much large size.\n#oott", "time": "12:40", "author": "IliaBouchouev", "author_name": "Dr. Ilia Bouchouev", "followers": 19952, "views": 5514, "likes": 34, "replies": 2, "retweets": 8, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 6, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Neutral", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Prices/technicals"]}}, {"id": "2075234196982022430", "url": "https://x.com/avionsunantiqu1/status/2075234196982022430", "text": "China is building 11 new strategic oil storage sites, while India plans  to more than double strategic petroleum reserve capacity. The Philippines is also  developing a national strategic petroleum reserve #OOTT\n https://t.co/iHUKLUo8zy via @BOEReport", "time": "15:02", "author": "avionsunantiqu1", "author_name": "Nicholas James", "followers": 1433, "views": 10922, "likes": 27, "replies": 2, "retweets": 5, "quotes": 3, "bookmarks": 6, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bullish", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Demand outlook"]}}, {"id": "2075247700958945776", "url": "https://x.com/antonisbabo/status/2075247700958945776", "text": "#oott outfit of the ton hahah https://t.co/dt8M983iLv", "time": "15:56", "author": "antonisbabo", "author_name": "바보", "followers": 39618, "views": 15010, "likes": 593, "replies": 0, "retweets": 204, "quotes": 13, "bookmarks": 34, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Neutral", "emotional_sentiment": "Positive", "topics": []}}, {"id": "2075253180883927131", "url": "https://x.com/DB_WTI/status/2075253180883927131", "text": "#OOTT #WTI \n#Tanker Attacks Risk Overplaying #Iran’s Hand and Reigniting a #War https://t.co/F84nd7jRfE", "time": "16:18", "author": "DB_WTI", "author_name": "WTI Trading Group- 🇺🇸 US Crude Oil Trader🛢️🌎", "followers": 12439, "views": 1634, "likes": 0, "replies": 0, "retweets": 0, "quotes": 2, "bookmarks": 0, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bullish", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Iran", "Tankers/shipping"]}}, {"id": "2075266409056080339", "url": "https://x.com/crudegusher/status/2075266409056080339", "text": "Well I figured if the President watches the show, might as well get on a soap box #OIL #OOTT #REFINING $VLO $DK #NATGAS", "time": "17:10", "author": "crudegusher", "author_name": "Sankey Research", "followers": 29287, "views": 23581, "likes": 120, "replies": 12, "retweets": 9, "quotes": 3, "bookmarks": 15, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Neutral", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Prices/technicals"]}}, {"id": "2075277509793550415", "url": "https://x.com/staunovo/status/2075277509793550415", "text": "The Fight Over Hormuz Boils Down to One Poorly Worded Clause in Trump’s Deal\nParagraph 5 hands Iran a leading role in opening the waterway, but one the U.S. and its allies aren’t comfortable with\n#oott https://t.co/jOs0u1gqee", "time": "17:54", "author": "staunovo", "author_name": "Giovanni Staunovo🛢", "followers": 120883, "views": 9534, "likes": 6, "replies": 1, "retweets": 1, "quotes": 3, "bookmarks": 0, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bullish", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Iran", "Tankers/shipping"]}}, {"id": "2075295047428272516", "url": "https://x.com/JavierBlas/status/2075295047428272516", "text": "MUST READ: “… But if we assume the Strait of Hormuz will remain at least partially open to ships and particularly oil tankers, the short-term impact of the war has not been cataclysmic….”\n\nhttps://t.co/BjUmkkB6mT", "time": "19:04", "author": "JavierBlas", "author_name": "Javier Blas", "followers": 393796, "views": 30226, "likes": 109, "replies": 7, "retweets": 13, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 31, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bearish", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Tankers/shipping", "Geopolitics"]}}, {"id": "2075296505460674820", "url": "https://x.com/ZmansEnrgyBrain/status/2075296505460674820", "text": "Oil started to react to the explosions and then retraced down $2+ when the U.S. said, \"not it\".  \n\nGulf states or Israel firing on Iran is far riskier for oil markets than U.S. Love Taps. \n\n#OOTT", "time": "19:10", "author": "ZmansEnrgyBrain", "author_name": "Z4 Energy Research", "followers": 11920, "views": 3650, "likes": 44, "replies": 5, "retweets": 5, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 0, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bearish", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Iran", "Prices/technicals"]}}, {"id": "2075328498420343051", "url": "https://x.com/Javi